Database structure:
-Table workspoints - all point
-Table oborudovanie - all equipments
-Table works - all works

Table workspoints structure:
-point_id INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
-point_name TEXT NOT NULL,
-point_address TEXT NOT NULL

Table oborudovanie structure:
id	INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
point_id	INTEGER NOT NULL,
name	TEXT NOT NULL,
model	TEXT NOT NULL,
serial_num	TEXT NOT NULL,
pre_id	INTEGER

Table works structure:
id	INTEGER NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
id_obor	INTEGER NOT NULL,
date	TEXT NOT NULL,
problem	TEXT NOT NULL,
result	TEXT